{"tid":1260002,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] IGN投票：最受期待PS獨占遊戲 《最後的生還者2》奪冠、FF7重製版第二、對馬島之魂第三","createTime":"2019-06-26T17:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T08:14:12.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b5018888a629ab62f4c0d9c9a0e2a39e738252a5","tid":1260002,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:32:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2367129983557509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2367129983557509&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=23b60d4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2367129983557509</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfZbGLh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfZbGLh.png&h=686f2126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>IGN投票：《最後的生還者2》為最受期待PS獨占遊戲</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  因為接下來有多款平台獨占 3A 大作即將登陸 PS4，知名媒體 IGN 近日做了一個小調查，根據玩家投票結果??顯示，《最後的生還者2》（The Last Of Us Part 2）為最受期待的 PlayStation 獨占遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n  據悉，此次共有2萬餘人參與了此次投票，在所有四款遊戲中，《最後的生還者2》以43.1%的得票率高居榜首，《最終幻想7重製版》（Final Fantasy VII Remake）佔比28.8%排第二，排第三的是《對馬島之鬼》（Ghost Of Tsushima）14.8%，小島新作《死亡擱淺》（Death Stranding）僅獲得13.3%的支持率。<br />\n<br />\n  這裡稍微提一下，除開《最終幻想7》不談，根據之前Sony發布的信息，《對馬島之鬼》、《最後的生還者2》、《死亡擱淺》都是會登陸 PS4 的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sKrvDM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sKrvDM.png&h=a9c5601c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4DfimLs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4DfimLs.png&h=35fb04a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n[女裝劇情還在] 本周Fami通雜志《最終幻想 7 重制版》導演野村哲也采訪要點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1244058/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1244058/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[PS4] 股東報告疑洩露《對馬島之魂》《The Last of Us Part II》將會在2020年3月前推出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240842/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240842/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"193e11acdd2a70c6fd5a1c0da5c7b5c39dcabdc2","tid":1260002,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T21:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8acf632b248aafd8dff3ccbf795fa057177c71","tid":1260002,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T23:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18baa5edf26414fb93995e9a2c3ea7b0aaf874a","tid":1260002,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15985128fec2586527386d8c0ca25c75999a8558","tid":1260002,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"當初買ps3都係為咗last of us<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16667e8bcb3a02b59e0d0cfc9e96e227315fd18","tid":1260002,"uid":213803,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:04:45.000Z","msg":"last of us有咩好玩 上星期第一次玩 冇咩feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b823174d7f8288f20b4ac7dab12b563960e598","tid":1260002,"uid":75449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"仆街全部下年3月出"},{"pid":"8dbc55dce9e4f64b1f4e0c2834cf5cae624bc480","tid":1260002,"uid":266716,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b16667e8bcb3a02b59e0d0cfc9e96e227315fd18","tid":1260002,"uid":213803,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:04:45.000Z","msg":"last of us有咩好玩 上星期第一次玩 冇咩feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:31:25.000Z","msg":"你今次仆街啦 襯個post冇乜人睇好快啲走啦"},{"pid":"40e4566a2719f2e9b9e3a3bded8bcc1b6ff38a35","tid":1260002,